00:21:56.659 --> 00:22:03.149
everywhere in Middle Eastern cooking. Israeli
chefs adopted it. They use it in very creative

00:22:03.149 --> 00:22:09.110
ways. We make all kind of flavored dressings
with that and you should learn how to use

00:22:09.110 --> 00:22:16.249
it. It's wonderful substitute for mayonnaise;
100%cholesterol free, very healthy, very calorie

